ns"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A style source identifier.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"sourceId"},{"name":"features","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The GeoJSON features to be updated in the source."}]}]},{"name":"dataId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The update operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"code":"onSourceDataLoaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter to filter the events)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onMapLoadingError"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"code":"type = metadata","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if data parsing error has occurred.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragra